text: Shigeaki Uchino was a modern pentathlete from Japan. Shigeaki competed at the 1960 and 1964 Summer Olympics. He was born on January 20, 1931 and died on January 14, 2016.Shigeaki Uchino == References == Category:1931 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Olympians for Japan Category:Japanese modern pentathletes Category:People from Miyazaki Prefecture
